videos.headline: UL Monroe punter gifts TD to Liberty
videos.description: UL Monroe punter Daniel Sparks fumbles the ball in the end zone directly into the hands of Liberty's Treon Sibley for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UL Monroe punter gifts TD to Liberty) 2020/10/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Liberty blocks punt in the end zone for a TD
videos.description: Liberty blocks UL Monroe's punt attempt and Treon Sibley quickly reacts and jumps on the ball to extend the Flames' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Liberty blocks punt in the end zone for a TD) 2020/10/10 ESHEET
